message.raw:
Added andor_structures.py (for some reason left behind) and also modified
andor_capabilities.py using enum.IntEnum subclasses for quick comparison with
AndorCaps. Added support to check_capabilities method in andor_utils and other
related changes. Removed _AC from andor_solis.py since it was not being used
at all.
